title: Annual Hang Seng index performance 1986 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Index points, containing a total of 34 data points.
In general Index points has rose over the Year.
The chart in general has a zig-zag shape.
The line rapidly decreased by 90.89% from Year '19 to '86, and lastly, increased by 115.67% from Year '92 to '93.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year '19 and '86.
The highest Index points, of value 29919.15 was reached at Year '17
The lowest Index points, of value 2302.75 was reported at Year '87
